[
  {
    "_comments": [
      "MJ Forms admin/builder Explorer application. Two Custom nav surfaces are driver",
      "classes registered by WP-D (the form builder/admin) and WP-F (the reporting",
      "dashboard) in MJExplorer; until those land the items render once their resources",
      "are registered. The Records nav item browses the Forms entity directly via MJ's",
      "generated entity forms. The embedded Application Entities make the Forms admin",
      "entities visible/browsable within this application."
    ],
    "fields": {
      "Name": "Forms",
      "Description": "Build, distribute, and analyze forms, surveys, and intake. Author forms with the visual builder or AI, publish public/embed/QR distributions, and review responses as first-class MemberJunction records.",
